---
title: Quick Creamy Pork, Bacon & Courgette Fusilli with Parmesan Cheese
description: In this dish, we've paired a special seasoning straight from Nan's secret spice drawer with a silky cream-based sauce, then followed it up with tender pork mince for a quick meal that looks and smells every bit as good as it tastes.
We’ve replaced the spaghetti in this recipe with fusilli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/668221e769536469029406ac-adffc63b.jpeg
